    <main id="main-content">
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="issue-hero" style="background-image: url('assets/images/placeholder-hero.jpg');">
            <div class="issue-hero-overlay"></div>
            <div class="container">
                <div class="issue-hero-content">
                    <h1>Executive Office of the President</h1>
                    <p class="issue-hero-description">Supporting President Barbie with expert guidance, policy coordination, and strategic leadership across the doll government.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Overview Section -->
        <section class="issue-overview-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="issue-overview-content">
                    <h2>About the EOP</h2>
                    <p>The Executive Office of the President (EOP) consists of the immediate staff of President Barbie, along with entities such as the Office of Management and Budget and the Office of Science and Technology Policy. The EOP is responsible for communicating the President's message to the doll community and promoting our fabulous priorities both domestically and globally.</p>
                    <p>The offices and councils within the EOP have responsibility for developing and implementing the economic, domestic, and national security policies that will make every doll's dreams come true. From managing the federal budget to advancing cutting-edge science and technology, the EOP ensures President Barbie's vision becomes reality.</p>
                    <p>These offices work collaboratively to address the most pressing challenges facing doll communities, coordinate policy across government agencies, and support the President in making informed decisions that benefit all dolls.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- EOP Offices Grid -->
        <section class="initiatives-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Principal Offices</h2>
                <div class="initiatives-grid">
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <a href="office-management-budget.html" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
                            <span class="initiative-icon">📊</span>
                            <h3>Office of Management and Budget</h3>
                            <p>Overseeing federal budget preparation, evaluating agency programs, and ensuring efficient resource allocation across the doll government.</p>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <a href="office-science-technology.html" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
                            <span class="initiative-icon">🔬</span>
                            <h3>Office of Science and Technology Policy</h3>
                            <p>Advancing scientific research, promoting innovation, and ensuring dream technology benefits all doll communities.</p>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <a href="council-economic-advisors.html" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
                            <span class="initiative-icon">💰</span>
                            <h3>Council of Economic Advisors</h3>
                            <p>Analyzing economic trends, providing expert guidance on fiscal policy, and supporting prosperity for all dolls.</p>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <a href="office-cyber-director.html" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
                            <span class="initiative-icon">🔐</span>
                            <h3>Office of the National Cyber Director</h3>
                            <p>Protecting doll data and digital infrastructure, coordinating cybersecurity strategy across government and private sectors.</p>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <a href="office-drug-control.html" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
                            <span class="initiative-icon">🏥</span>
                            <h3>Office of National Drug Control Policy</h3>
                            <p>Promoting wellness, preventing harmful substances, and ensuring healthy, vibrant doll communities nationwide.</p>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <a href="council-environmental-quality.html" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
                            <span class="initiative-icon">🌱</span>
                            <h3>Council on Environmental Quality</h3>
                            <p>Advancing environmental protection, climate action, and sustainable practices for green dreamhouses everywhere.</p>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Mission Statement -->
        <section class="impact-stats-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <div class="priorities-content" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
                    <p class="priorities-text">The Executive Office of the President exists to serve President Barbie and, through her, all dolls across the nation. We coordinate policy development, ensure efficient government operations, provide expert analysis and advice, and work tirelessly to implement the President's vision for a more fabulous, equitable, and prosperous future for every doll.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

